<p class="subheading noPspace header"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 49px; line-height: 49px;">New Beginnings</span></p>
<p class="noPspace subheading">Help restore hope to families making a fresh start.&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace">Imagine taking a shower and not having a towel, or trying to prepare a meal without pots, pans, plates or utensils. New Beginnings works with families in our community who need these household essentials. We don&rsquo;t just give them stuff; we connect with the families, build relationships with them and get to know their unique circumstances. Then we help fill their home with hope, trust and love, as well as needed household items.</p>
<p class="noPspace">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace">If you&rsquo;d like to show God&rsquo;s love to a family making a new beginning, there are lots of ways you can help:</p>
<p class="noPspace">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace"><strong>Serve</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace">Flexible serving opportunities are available. Opportunities include moving, decorating, organizing supplies, cleaning and making household repairs.</p>
<p class="noPspace">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace"><strong>Donate</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace">We&rsquo;re looking for new or gently used furniture and household items. We&rsquo;re talking about nice stuff here, people&mdash;things you wouldn&rsquo;t be embarrassed to display or use in your own house. Commonly needed items are:</p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">-Furniture</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">-Kitchenware: pots, pans, utensils, appliances, etc.</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">-Fans (ceiling or box)</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">-Portable heaters and air conditioners</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">-Bed linens (any size)</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">-Bathroom essentials</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">-</span><span style="line-height: 1.75;">Home decorations</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;"><span style="font-family: arial, sans-serif;">Drop off gently-used items at the&nbsp;Crossroads&nbsp;Oakley Annex on the 1st &amp; 3rd&nbsp;</span>Saturday of the month from&nbsp;10-1pm and the 1st &amp; 3rd&nbsp;Tuesday from 5-7:30pm.</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="noPspace"><strong>Sign up at the Info Center or&nbsp;<a title="Email New Beginnings" href="/mysend/208">email us to get connected to the New Beginnings team</a>.</strong></p>